{
  "style": "IEEE",
  "texts": [
    "By using logistic regression, the model provides probabilistic interpretations of safe WCET ranges, while the GA explores the space of possible WCET values to identify those likely to cause deadline misses.",
    "This combined approach improves the estimation of safe WCET ranges, even in the early stages of system design, facilitating better decision-making for engineers.Kumar [92] presents an approach for early WCET estimation using deep neural networks (DNNs).",
    "Traditional WCET estimation methods require the hardware and compiled application code, which are only available in the final stages of system development.",
    "The proposed DNN-based method predicts WCET directly from the source code, bypassing the need for hardware execution.",
    "The model is trained using the PyTorch framework, leveraging features extracted with the SWEET tool [93], which counts various operations in the source code."
  ],
